Liabilities:
\ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ $1\ \ liabilities:debts
\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-
\ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ $1

Equity:
\ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ $1\ \ equity:owner
\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-
\ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ $1

Total:
\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-
\ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ 0
\f[]
.fi
